{"tid":59424,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"大家 coding 上做過或見過咩on9野","createTime":"2016-12-29T15:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-09T11:26:24.000Z","uid":58358,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a6b2046bbda992fa450d71766cf1007d506f932c","tid":59424,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:31:11.000Z","msg":"話說今日要寫個 accordion UI component<br />\n<br />\n咁我就<br />\neach( list, item =&gt; item.onPress(event =&gt; {<br />\n    each( list, item =&gt; item.collapse(true) );<br />\n    item.collapse(false);<br />\n})<br />\n// performance 勁差<br />\n<br />\n但其實只要<br />\nlet expandedItem;<br />\neach( list, item =&gt; item.onPress(event =&gt; {<br />\n    expandedItem &amp;&amp; expandedItem.collapse(true);<br />\n    item.collapse(false);<br />\n    expandedItem = item;<br />\n})<br />\n// 即刻順返曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cacf17dd7885dc2990e9587bd1e09986e84c2bde","tid":59424,"uid":11077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T16:44:24.000Z","msg":"將0 打左做o"},{"pid":"d67e61b2314364c4cd2173030cfe480adcb55e79","tid":59424,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T16:59:32.000Z","msg":"唔知有Emmet存在, 逐粒字打HTML/CSS code打咗十幾廿年! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d361626afd64bbb7ffc07866ae554361c188f711","tid":59424,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:01:40.000Z","msg":"I-&gt;l"},{"pid":"c3d91727895c501e3bb3bc3b7a58eba8cb447817","tid":59424,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:02:28.000Z","msg":"; ⬅️開頭學Java成日打漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4721c42aea80e5e62b90531d1e4f75702241d141","tid":59424,"uid":34165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:07:31.000